channel.title: Medieval Project IV
channel.description:
Medieval Project IV is Here (final version)
why is it the final version you may ask? because i have stopped hosting due to a wireless router problem and have decided to stop coding but maybe in the future there will be a new medieval saga.
what will you find in medievalproject?
Just to state first off, This is not based off deltascape but uses the same base that delta used (devo 7-8)
-pest control -fight caves -fight pits -membership -member items -anti syi -anti null -over 6 quests -rangers now get drops -godsword specials -classes -minigames -training areas -well thought out shops -crystal bow degrading -damaged items (read below to find out what they are). -warriors guild -over 10 fully constructed towns -working prayer -tab switch (read below) -custom client -void set effect (on players) -vengeance (bit bugged) -great pking -GodWars -Clue Scrolls -auto retaliate -all working emotions (only on the client emote tab) -much more
Damaged Items?
Damaged items are given to new players as a taste of the real thing
i.e if you choose warrior you will get a whip this whip will last 1k shots so will every other item that is damaged, they give the same stats as there real form but break and disappear forever!
Tab Switch?
Most people don't use your set client am i right? so i give them the option of either using the old silab tabs or use the clients set tabs, the set tabs giving a few more bonuses (such as piety or working emotions).
